long.am,bn,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,fa,fi,:
Draw directly on any webpage once you install this extension.

Want a quick way to make comments/review any web page? Want to make notes on any website? You can use this extension to take notes and review any specific webpage.

Features include

- Take a screenshot of the current webpage you are on before you begin drawing
- Use our pencil tool to draw freehand on any webpage
- Add in text and arrows to highlight specific areas
- Add in shapes such as rectangles and circles
- Adjust the thickness and color of your paint brush
- Erase/Undo any mistakes

This is a fast and simple tool to markup/make remarks for any webpage before you save it onto your computer.

Send feedback quickly to team members using this simple markup tool.

Disclaimer: Please note this extension is NOT made by Google and is made by an independent development team. All copyrights belong to their respective owners.
Google doesn’t endorse or sponsor this extension. Page Markup for Google Chrome™ is not owned by, is not licensed by and is not a subsidiary of Google Inc.
